            <id>/particles/core-theming/colors/</id>
            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="w-100 flex flex-wrap center bg-grays-white pa2">
    <div class="cf w-100 flex flex-wrap">
        <div class="bg-wcag-primary   ma2 pa2 tc w4 fl">Primary<p>#262324</p></div>
        <div class="bg-wcag-secondary ma2 pa2 tc w4 fl">Secondary<p>#bed000</p></div>
        <div class="bg-wcag-accent1   ma2 pa2 tc w4 fl">Accent 1<p>#00bed0</p></div>
        <div class="bg-wcag-accent2   ma2 pa2 tc w4 fl">Accent 2<p>#bf13bc</p></div>
        <div class="bg-wcag-accent3   ma2 pa2 tc w4 fl">Accent 3<p>#5f5aa2</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="w-100">About these colors</h2>
    <p>Many web applications use standard patterns for color palettes. This implementation has been designed to allow for an extensible color palette.
        You can find the input values in <a class="tag tag-accent3" href="/particles/core-utility/variables/">_variables.scss</a>.</p>

    <p>Be aware that some components require specific modifiers such as light4 or light to work. Abiding to this pattern is a design choice
    I made for my components.</p>
<pre class="w-100"><code>     bg         = background color
    -[color]
    -[color]-[tone]
    -wcag-[color]-[tone]

c          = color
    -[color]
    -[color]-[tone]

bg-wcag    = WCAG compliant contrast background
             and defined light and copy text colors.
    -[color]
    -[color]-[tone]

hgl        = Highlight (40% opacity of base)
    -[color]

hover-bg   = Hover background color
    -[color]
    -[color]-[tone]

hover      = Hover text color
    -[color]
    -[color]-[tone]

c-inherit  = inherit text color from parent
</code></pre>
    <h2 class="w-100 mt1">Default classes</h2>
<pre><code>Base colors don't require a [tone] modifier.
    bg-gray-base becomes bg-gray

    background color:       bg-[color]-[tone]
    text-color:             c-[color]-[tone]
    wcag text & background: bg-wcag-[color]-[tone]
    hover bg:               hover-bg-[color]-[tone]
    hover text:             hover-[color]-[tone]
    highlight bg:           hgl-[color]             only base colors
</code></pre>
    <p class="w-100">All available colors are listed below with high contrast text.</p>

    <h2 class="w-100 mt1">Brand colors with accents</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-column ma1">
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-primary-light3"> primary-light3   <span class="f6">#BEBDBD</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-primary-light2"> primary-light2   <span class="f6">#939192</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-primary-light1"> primary-light1   <span class="f6">#514F50</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-primary">        primary-base     <span class="f6">#262324</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-primary-dark1">  primary-dark1    <span class="f6">#1B1919</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-column ma1">
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-light4"> secondary-light4   <span class="f6">#F9FAE6</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-light3"> secondary-light3   <span class="f6">#ECF1B3</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-light2"> secondary-light2   <span class="f6">#DFE880</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-light1"> secondary-light1   <span class="f6">#CBD933</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary">        secondary-base     <span class="f6">#bed000</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-dark1">  secondary-dark1    <span class="f6">#ABBB00</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-dark2">  secondary-dark2    <span class="f6">#859200</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-dark3">  secondary-dark3    <span class="f6">#5F6800</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-secondary-dark4">  secondary-dark4    <span class="f6">#393E00</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-column ma1">
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-light4"> accent1-light4   <span class="f6">#E6F9FA</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-light3"> accent1-light3   <span class="f6">#B3ECF1</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-light2"> accent1-light2   <span class="f6">#80DFE8</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-light1"> accent1-light1   <span class="f6">#4DD2DE</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1">        accent1-base     <span class="f6">#00bed0</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-dark1">  accent1-dark1    <span class="f6">#0098A6</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-dark2">  accent1-dark2    <span class="f6">#00727D</span></div>
        <div class="pa2 tc w4 bg-wcag-accent1-dark3">  accent1-dark3    <span class="f6">#004C53</span></div>
